 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


2009




Headquarters


Clifton House, 75 Fort Street, Grand Cayman, George Town Ky-1108




Type of Company



                                                                    Public
                                                            




Employees (Worldwide)


7,800




Industries


Apparel & Footwear




Company Description


Cosmo Lady (China) Holdings Co. Ltd. operates as an investment holding company which engages in the manufacture and sale of intimate wear. It operates through the following brands: Cosmo Lady, Cosmo Elegance, Cosmo Blossom, and Cosmo Esquire. The Cosmo Lady brand targets fashion-conscious women with ages between twenty five to thirty five. The Cosmo Elegance brand concentrates on affluent women with ages between thirty five to forty five. The Cosmo Blossom brand focuses on young women with ages between fourteen to twenty five. The Cosmo Esquire brand targets men consumers with ages between eighteen to forty five. The company was founded by Zheng Yao Nan on January 28, 2014 and is headquartered in Dongguan, China.




Website


http://www.cosmo-lady.com.hk/






